comments: Hampton (ORL) briefly places and removes a marginal hand from Mitchell's (SAC) body on the perimeter.
Wagner (ORL) establishes himself in a screening position in Mitchell's (SAC) path and marginal contact occurs as he rolls to the basket.
Hampton (ORL) makes direct contact with the ball and part of Jones' (SAC) hand that is on the ball during the layup attempt.
Bamba (ORL) places his left arm on Lyles' (SAC) body as both players move toward the rebound, and the contact is marginal.
DiVincenzo (SAC) leans in slightly and makes marginal contact with the chest of Hampton (ORL), and Hampton's reaction is not commensurate with the level of contact.
Jones (SAC) establishes himself in a legal screening position in the path of Hampton (ORL) and absorbs some marginal contact during the pick.
Hampton's (ORL) shoulder grazes DiVincenzo's (SAC) shorts and the marginal touch has no impact on the perimeter jump shot attempt.
Jones (SAC) places a marginal forearm on Wagner's (ORL) side during the driving shot attempt.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Bamba (ORL) dislodges the ball out of bounds. There is no clear and conclusive angle showing that Jones (SAC) made the last contact with the ball.
Wagner (ORL) makes contact with the ball that dislodges it from Mitchell (SAC) prior to incidental contact occurring on the driving shot attempt.
Okeke's (ORL) fingertips graze the wrist of Lyles (SAC), who is unaffected by the marginal contact during the layup attempt near the rim.
DiVincenzo (SAC) commits a take foul on Wagner (ORL).
Mitchell (SAC) gets his fingertips to the ball and cleanly deflects Anthony's (ORL) dribble.
Bamba (ORL) establishes himself in a legal screening position and some incidental contact occurs with Mitchell (SAC) during the pick.
Jones (SAC) ends his dribble and maintains a legal pivot foot during his turnaround shot attempt.
Barnes (SAC) and Wagner (ORL) entangle and soon thereafter unwind their arms during the rebounding opportunity, and the contact is marginal.
Bamba (ORL) establishes himself in a screening position in Barnes' (SAC) path during the pick and both players continue to engage thereafter.
Jones (SAC) makes marginal contact with Wagner's (ORL) arm after his release on the shot attempt.
Anthony (ORL) and Holiday (SAC) engage and disengage during the inbounds play, and the contact is marginal.
Anthony (ORL) commits a take foul on Jones (SAC).
DiVincenzo (SAC) establishes himself in a wide screening position in Hampton's (ORL) path, and the contact is marginal.
Anthony (ORL) commits a take foul on DiVincenzo (SAC).
Wagner (ORL) is firming up in Mitchell's (SAC) path with his arms slightly extended during the screen, and the contact is marginal.
Mitchell (SAC) legally contests Wagner's (ORL) shot attempt in the lane.
